{"tid":2109932,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我諗到個唔使戴口罩都可以令身邊嘅人都可以安嘅方法","createTime":"2020-07-15T13:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T14:13:50.000Z","uid":26689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7b788d2178f2753c350ca1a406b2760aa907a269","tid":2109932,"uid":26689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T13:59:33.000Z","msg":"老實講 其實我一直都唔鍾戴口罩  但我又怕死<br />\n咁無辦法要戴啦   而我係認為出條法案可以豁免戴口罩  就係好似考牌唔使帶狗罩<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/94gkOde.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F94gkOde.jpg&h=4ef43e34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就建議整張「良民證」 個額頭釘住個肺炎化驗結果  每三個鐘檢查更新一次資料  如果有病或更新唔切就直接用北韓疫苗解決  一粒子彈解決病情  畢竟有啲人選擇堅持唔戴口罩一定有苦衷嘅  佢地一定唔介意做多步嘅   所以大家唔好迫人戴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jSa2g77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjSa2g77.jpg&h=8a868019&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\">（衛生署正在清理受感染的人）</span>"},{"pid":"f277bc9a66a8d231238ac4dea6f31f2e6604d831","tid":2109932,"uid":26689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T14:13:50.000Z","msg":"標題打漏咗  應該係安心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 今年諾貝爾和平同醫學獎仲唔係我<br />\n文學獎應該無了"}]}